每项的名称
leadmonom, leadexp, lead, leadcoef, f-lead (f) Global ordering , local ordering, mixed ordering global lp (4,1,1)&gt;(3,3,2) because 4&gt;3
dp (3,3,2)&gt;(4,1,1) because 4+1+1&lt;3+3+2 若次数相等, 则从后比起, 小在前 Dp 从前比, 打在前. Local p (polynomial) 换成 s (seris), 次数高的后置即可. <a data-href="Singular Lecture 2" href="代数/singular/singular-lecture-2.html#_0" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">Singular Lecture 2</a>
